import React from 'react'
import { NavLink, Link } from 'react-router-dom'
import { Card, CardBody, CardLink, ListGroup, Nav } from 'reactstrap'

const Navbar = () => {
  return (
    <Nav className='navlink pt-5 pb-5 '>
      

      <ListGroup>
        
      </ListGroup>
      
       <CardLink><Link to='/' > Home </Link></CardLink> 
      <Link to='addreview' > Add Review </Link>
      <Link to='viewreviews' > View Reviews </Link>
       
      
      
    </Nav>
  )
}

export default Navbar
